lead_paragraph: Officials said they thought it unlikely that two United States residents of Yemeni descent held in Amsterdam on Monday had any connection to terrorism.
snippet: Officials said they thought it unlikely that two United States residents of Yemeni descent held in Amsterdam on Monday had any connection to terrorism.

headline.main: Terrorist Ties Doubted in Amsterdam Arrests
headline.seo: 2 Yemenis Detained in Amsterdam Found Unconnected to Terrorism
headline.print_headline: Detained Yemenis Are Thought to Be Unconnected to Terrorism, Officials Say
